Innovation Features Added to the Movie App

1. Duplicate Favourite Prevention

An additional validation feature was implemented to prevent users from adding the same movie multiple times to the
 favourites list.Before adding a movie to favourites, the application checks whether the movie already exists in local 
 storage using the movie ID.If the movie already exists, the application displays an alert message instead of storing 
 duplicate entries.

Benefits:
- Improves user experience
- Prevents duplicate movie entries
- Keeps favourites list organised
- Demonstrates validation logic


2. Interactive Actor and Crew Navigation

Additional navigation functionality was added to improve application interactivity.

Users can:
- Click cast members
- Click crew members
- View actor details
- Browse other movies associated with actors

This functionality was implemented using Angular routing and TMDB API integration.

Benefits:
- Enhances movie exploration
- Improves navigation experience
- Adds functionality beyond the core assignment requirements
- Demonstrates dynamic routing and API integration skills


Conclusion

These innovations were implemented to improve usability, interactivity, and overall 
application quality beyond the minimum assignment requirements.